# Design System Rules

Tokens are derived from the Figma file and defined in `tailwind.config.js` +
`src/css/main.css`. **Never invent colors, sizes, or fonts** — use the tokens
below. If something is missing, add it to the config first.

## Colors (Figma "Primary dark palette" + "Accent Usage")

Dark scale: `ink` (DEFAULT `#0B0F1A`, `ink-light`, `ink-mid`), `slate`, `steel`,
`muted`, `soft`, `cloud`, `fog`, `paper`, plus `white`.
Accent: `accent` (DEFAULT `#00D4AA`, `accent-bright`, `accent-dim`, `accent/15`
for glow). Brand: `brand-teal`, `brand-navy`.
Back-compat aliases: `neutral-*` and `brand-*` (50–950) mirror the `ink` scale.

## Typography

- `font-display` → **Syne** (700, 800) — headings, hero, stats, logo.
- `font-body`    → **DM Sans** (400/500/600/700) — everything else.
- Type scale: `text-h1` 56, `text-h2` 44, `text-h3` 20, `text-body` 16,
  `text-small` 14, `text-label` 11. Legacy `text-display-*` still work.

## Spacing & layout

- Figma scale: `xs` 4, `sm` 8, `md` 16, `lg` 24, `xl` 40, `2xl` 64, `3xl` 100,
  `4xl` 140. Works on `p-*`, `m-*`, `gap-*`, `py-*`, etc.
- Max content width: `1200px` → use `.container-snz` or `max-w-content`.
- Section rhythm: `py-section` (100px), `py-section-sm` (64px).

## Components (preferred classes)

Use these semantic classes instead of inline utility soup:

- Buttons: `btn-primary` (accent), `btn-outline` (ink), `btn-ghost`.
- Tags: `tag-industry`, `tag-technology`.
- Filter chips: `chip` + `aria-pressed="true"` or `.is-active`.
- Forms: `form-input`, `form-select`, `form-textarea`, `form-label`.
- Sections: `section`, `section-dark`, `section-muted`, `cta-banner`.
- Cards: `card`, `card-notch`, `card-dark`, `card-body`.
- Prose (WP editor output): wrap with `.prose-snz`.

## Mechanical notch motif

Signature bevel. Apply `notch-xs` (8px), `notch-sm` (12px), `notch-md` (16px),
or `notch`/`notch-lg` (28px) on buttons, chips, tags, and cards. Ghost buttons
intentionally have no notch.

## Dot grid

`bg-dot-grid-dark` / `bg-dot-grid-light` with the default 24×24 pattern, or
the ready-made `cta-banner` (ink + white dots overlay).

## Accessibility

- Use `.skip-link` for skip-to-content.
- Focus styles are global (accent ring); inherit `ring-offset-ink` on dark
  sections (already handled in CSS).

## Anti-patterns

- ❌ Raw hex colors in templates (`class="bg-[#00D4AA]"`).
- ❌ Arbitrary typography sizes (`text-[56px]`) — use `text-h1`.
- ❌ `rounded-*` on buttons/chips/cards that should carry the notch motif.
- ❌ Stacking `px-6 py-3 bg-accent text-ink font-bold ...` manually — use `btn-primary`.
